nd databases on to a single platform, allowing customers to access all the Group&#8217;s loan offerings on a single platform, thereby maximizing our cross-selling opportunities.&#8221;</em></p></li><li><p><em>Nothing in this post is to be considered investment advice.</em></p></li></ol><div class="subscription-widget-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://theindianpivot.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe&quot;,&quot;language&quot;:&quot;en&quot;}" data-component-name="SubscribeWidgetToDOM"><div class="subscription-widget show-subscribe"><div class="preamble"><p class="cta-caption"><strong>Final Subscribe CTA #3</strong></p></div><form class="subscription-widget-subscribe"><input type="email" class="email-input" name="email" placeholder="Type your email&#8230;" tabindex="-1"><input type="submit" class="button primary" value="Subscribe"><div class="fake-input-wrapper"><div class="fake-input"></div><div class="fake-button"></div></div></form></div></div>